=== 海军训练、早期分配、首次婚姻和孩子 ===
从军校毕业后，麦凯恩获委任为[[少尉|少尉]]<ref name="milrec-bio">{{cite web | title = John McCain's Navy Records: Biographical Data | publisher = United States Navy | accessdate = 2008-11-01 | archivedate = 2008-11-01 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20081101084453/http://www.npc.navy.mil/NR/rdonlyres/330F85C7-5982-4B09-A46A-373964430AFB/0/Document.pdf | format = PDF | deadurl = yes | url = http://www.npc.navy.mil/NR/rdonlyres/330F85C7-5982-4B09-A46A-373964430AFB/0/Document.pdf}}</ref><ref>{{cite news | url = http://www.boston.com/news/nation/articles/2008/05/07/navy_releases_mccains_military_record/ | title = Navy releases McCain's military record | last = Kuhnhenn | first = Jim | agency = Associated Press  | publisher = ''The Boston Globe'' | date = 2008-05-07 | accessdate = 2008-05-23 | archivedate = 2009-06-27 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090627082502/http://www.boston.com/news/nation/articles/2008/05/07/navy_releases_mccains_military_record/}}</ref>。他先在[[佛罗里达州|佛罗里达州]][[彭萨科拉海军航空站|彭萨科拉海军航空站]]接受海军飞行员训练至1959年9月，再到德克萨斯州[[科珀斯克里斯蒂海军航空站|科珀斯克里斯蒂海军航空站]]训练，训练过程为期两年，麦凯恩还在[[科珀斯克里斯蒂_(德克萨斯州)|科珀斯克里斯蒂]]受训期间晋升[[中尉|中尉]]<ref name="milrec-bio" /><ref name="Alexander-2002" />{{rp|32}}。他开的车是[[雪佛兰科尔维特|科尔维特]]，女友则是号称“佛罗里达烈焰玛丽”（{{lang|en|Marie the Flame of Florida}}）的[[艳舞女郎|艳舞女郎]]，每有闲余时间，他就会前去海滩，或是在军官宿舍房间改装的酒吧和只向熟人开放的赌局度过，是他人眼中整天沉迷聚会的人物，回首往事，麦凯恩称，那时他总体上是在随意挥霍自己的健康和青春<ref name="ap-wmd" /><ref name="Timberg-1999" />{{rp|66–68}}。由于缺乏耐心钻研飞行手册，反倒把时间花在研读历史书籍上，麦凯恩起初的飞行员成绩低于标准<ref name="wapo083108" /><ref name="Timberg-1999" />{{rp|66–68}}。受此影响，他没有分配到驾驶[[战斗机|战斗机]]的精英分队，而是成为[[强击机|强击机]]飞行员<ref name="wapo083108" />。1960年3月在德克萨斯州进行飞行训练时，他驾驶的飞机单人单活塞发动机[[A-1强击机|AD-6强击机]]因失速而坠入[[科珀斯克里斯蒂湾|科珀斯克里斯蒂湾]]（{{lang|en|Corpus Christi Bay}}）并沉至海底<ref name="lat100608">{{cite news | url = http://articles.latimes.com/2008/oct/06/nation/na-aviator6 | title = Mishaps mark John McCain's record as naval aviator | last1 = Vartabedian | first1 = Ralph | last2 = Serrano | first2 = Richard A. | publisher = ''Los Angeles Times'' | date = 2008-10-06 | accessdate = 2016-01-11 | archivedate = 2015-11-06 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151106220533/http://articles.latimes.com/2008/oct/06/nation/na-aviator6 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。坠机瞬间麦凯恩一度失去知觉，但很快就苏醒过来并成功打开驾驶舱游回数米之上的水面，并没有因这起事故受重伤<ref name="Alexander-2002" />{{rp|32}}<ref name="lat100608" />。1960年5月<ref name="milrec-bio" />，麦凯恩从科珀斯克里斯蒂的飞行学校毕业<ref name="Alexander-2002" />{{rp|32}}，然后前往弗吉尼亚州的[[奥西安纳海军航空站|奥西安纳海军航空站]]，接受为期5个月的进一步强击机飞行训练<ref name="milrec-bio" />。

从1960年11月开始，麦凯恩成为[[无畏号航空母舰|无畏号航空母舰]]和[[企业号航空母舰_(CVN-65)|企业号航空母舰]]<ref name="feinberg">{{cite book | last = Feinberg | first = Barbara Silberdick | title = John McCain: Serving His Country | url = https://archive.org/details/johnmccainservin00fein | publisher = Millbrook Press | year = 2000 | isbn = 0-7613-1974-3 | pages = [https://archive.org/details/johnmccainservin00fein/page/16 16], 18}}</ref>[[美国海军第65攻击中队|“世界著名战斗老虎”第65攻击中队]]的强击机飞行员<ref name="milrec-bio" /><ref name="McCain-Salter-1999" />{{rp|156}}，两艘航母的基地都是[[诺福克海军基地|诺福克海军基地]]<ref name="McCain-Salter-1999" />{{rp|156}}，除在[[加勒比海|加勒比海]]巡航外，还多次部署到[[地中海|地中海]]<ref name="Timberg-1999" />{{rp|66–68}}。麦凯恩的驾驶技术有所改善<ref name="Timberg-1999" />{{rp|66–68}}<ref name="lat100608" />，但就在1961年12月，他又在[[西班牙|西班牙]]南部上空因过于鲁莽地降低飞行高度而撞上输电线缆<ref name="lat100608" />，造成当地停电，不过他还是成功将受损的强击机开回无畏号航母<ref name="lat100608" />。

1962年1月，企业号航母展开处女航，麦凯恩的姓氏引起舰长注意，还成为船上其他官兵眼里的名人<ref name="lat100608" />。1962年6月，他升任上尉<ref name="milrec-bio" />，同年10月[[古巴导弹危机|古巴导弹危机]]爆发时，企业号协助执行海上封锁任务，麦凯恩在此期间负责在舰上发布警报<ref name="freeman">{{cite book | last = Freeman | first = Gregory A. | title = Sailors to the End: The Deadly Fire on the USS Forrestal and the Heroes Who Fought It | publisher = HarperCollins | year = 2002 | isbn = 0-06-093690-8 | page = 25}}</ref>。1963年11月，他被转回陆地，在彭萨科拉的海军航空兵基本训练指挥部服役9个月<ref name="milrec-bio" /><ref name="feinberg" />。1964年9月，他成为密西西比州[[梅瑞迪恩海军航空站|梅瑞迪恩海军航空站]]{{lang|en|VT}}-7训练中队的[[飞行教官|飞行教官]]<ref name="milrec-bio" /><ref name="Alexander-2002" />{{rp|33}}，这里还有以他爷爷命名的麦凯恩飞行场<ref>{{cite web | title = History | publisher = United States Navy | url = https://www.cnic.navy.mil/meridian/AboutCNIC/GeneralInformation/index.htm | accessdate = 2016-01-11 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150117221348/http://www.cnic.navy.mil/regions/cnrse/installations/nas_meridian/about/history.html | archivedate = 2015-01-17 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。

1964年进驻彭萨科拉期间，麦凯恩开始同来自[[宾夕法尼亚州|宾夕法尼亚州]][[费城|费城]]<ref name="Alexander-2002" />{{rp|32}}<ref name="Timberg-1999" />{{rp|66–68}}的泳装和{{lang|en|T}}形台模特卡罗尔·西普（{{lang|en|Carol Shepp}}）交往<ref name="dm060808">{{cite news | first = Sharon | last = Churcher | title = The wife U.S. Republican John McCain callously left behind | url = http://www.dailymail.co.uk/femail/article-1024927/The-wife-John-McCain-callously-left-behind.html | publisher = ''The Mail on Sunday'' | date = 2008-06-08 | accessdate = 2016-01-12 | location = London | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151120030337/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/femail/article-1024927/The-wife-John-McCain-callously-left-behind.html | archivedate = 2015-11-20}}</ref><ref name="wapo100608">{{cite news |title=The Separate Peace of John And Carol |last=Farhi |first=Paul |publisher=''The Washington Post'' |date=2008-10-06 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20130105053956/http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2008/10/05/AR2008100502589.html |url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2008/10/05/AR2008100502589.html |accessdate=2016-01-12 |archivedate=2013-01-05 }}</ref>。两人早在海军学院就已相识，她曾嫁给麦凯恩的同学，但之后离婚<ref name="Alexander-2002" />{{rp|32}}<ref name="feinberg" />。麦凯恩告诉西普，他有心要做一番大事业，以求将来青史留名<ref name="Kristof">{{cite news | url = http://www.nytimes.com/2000/02/27/us/pow-to-power-broker-a-chapter-most-telling.html | title = P.O.W. to Power Broker, A Chapter Most Telling | publisher = ''The New York Times'' | date = 2000-02-27 | last = Kristof | first = Nicholas | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151106220626/http://www.nytimes.com/2000/02/27/us/pow-to-power-broker-a-chapter-most-telling.html | archivedate = 2015-11-06 | accessdate = 2016-01-12}}</ref>。1965年7月3日，两人在费城完婚<ref name="dmr-mccain">{{cite web | url = http://www.azcentral.com/news/election/election08/articles/09170914elections08-mccain.html | title = Obama Inauguration: John McCain | newspaper = The Arizona Republic | accessdate = 2016-02-13}}</ref><ref name="old-timeline" />，西普之前已有两个孩子，长子道格拉斯生于1959年，次子安德鲁于1962年出生，两人于1966年成为麦凯恩的养子<ref name="old-timeline">{{cite web | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20000620034707/http://www.mccain2000.com/story/timeline.html | archivedate = 2000-06-20 | url = http://www.mccain2000.com/story/timeline.html | title = The John McCain Story: Timeline | publisher = McCain 2000, Inc | accessdate = 2000-06-20}}</ref><ref name="Timberg-1999" />{{rp|70}}。1966年9月，卡罗尔和约翰的女儿西德尼（{{lang|en|Sidney}}）出世<ref name="nyt122707">{{cite news | url = http://www.nytimes.com/2007/12/27/us/politics/27mccainkids.html | title = Bridging 4 Decades, a Large, Close-Knit Brood | last = Steinhauer | first = Jennifer | newspaper = ''The New York Times'' | date = 2016-01-12 | accessdate = 2016-01-12 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151106220535/http://www.nytimes.com/2007/12/27/us/politics/27mccainkids.html | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2015-11-06}}</ref>。1965年7月，麦凯恩参加[[阿特·弗莱明|阿特·弗莱明]]（{{lang|en|Art Fleming}}）主持的[[游戏节目|智力问答节目]]《[[危险边缘|危险边缘]]》，但只赢得一局比赛<ref>{{ cite news | last = Fouhy | first = Beth | title = Political Play: McCain recalls loss on "Jeopardy" | url = http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/news/politics/2008-06-30-2937395846_x.htm | agency = Associated Press | publisher = ''USA Today'' | date = 2008-06-30 | accessdate = 2016-01-12 | quote = Riding aboard his Straight Talk Express campaign bus, McCain, well-read and a trivia buff, recalled his two-day appearance on the popular program in 1965. He won the game the first day, and lost the next day in the final round. | archivedate = 2014-10-06 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141006103643/http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/news/politics/2008-06-30-2937395846_x.htm}}</ref><ref>{{ cite web | url = http://boards.sonypictures.com/boards/showthread.php?t=37250 | title = John McCain—Jeopardy! champion (Update) | publisher = Sony Pictures | accessdate = 2010-02-24 | quote = [McCain] defeated 1-time champion Peggy Fisher in Fleming #355, taped in Studio 6A 1965-07-20, aired Friday, 1965-08-06. In his next game, Fleming #356, taped in Studio 6A 1965-07-20, aired Monday, 1965-08-09, he was defeated by challenger Bob Bovard. | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20100224054620/http://boards.sonypictures.com/boards/showthread.php?t=37250 | archivedate = 2010-02-24 | deadurl = yes}}</ref>。

[[File:McCainWithSquadron.jpg|thumb]]，摄于1965年。]]

1965年11月，麦凯恩驾驶[[北美T-2巴克艾教练机|T-2教练机]]飞行至[[弗吉尼亚东海岸|弗吉尼亚东海岸]]上空时，飞机发动机出现严重故障，他在飞机坠毁前成功弹出，这已是他遭遇的第3次飞行事故<ref name="lat100608" />。驻扎梅瑞迪恩（{{lang|en|Meridian}}）时，麦凯恩主动请求出战<ref name="Timberg-1999" />{{rp|70–71}}。1966年10月，他成为参加[[越南战争|越南战争]]的预定人选，因此前往佛罗里达州的[[塞西尔菲尔德海军航空兵基地|塞西尔菲尔德海军航空兵基地]]向第44候补飞行中队报道，接受驾驶[[A-4天鹰式攻击机|A4天鹰]]单座喷气式强击机的训练<ref name="milrec-bio" /><ref name="Timberg-1999" />{{rp|70–71}}<ref name="McCain-Salter-1999" />{{rp|172–173}}。麦凯恩在这里的表现为他人看好，只是他在飞行时总试图要“[[飞行包线|挑战战机的飞行极限]]”<ref name="lat100608" />。1967年1月，麦凯恩晋升[[少校|少校]]<ref name="milrec-bio" />，再于同年5月成为[[福萊斯特號航空母艦|福萊斯特號航空母艦]]的一员<ref name="milrec-bio" />，隶属舰上的[[美国海军第46攻击中队|第46攻击中队]]<ref>{{cite web | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20081022113208/http://www.skyhawk.org/3e/va46/va46p.htm | archivedate = 2008-10-22 | url = http://www.skyhawk.org/3e/va46/va46p.htm | title = VA-46 Photograph Album | publisher = The Skyhawk Association | accessdate = 2008-10-22}}</ref>。这年春季，福萊斯特號航空母艦都在大西洋演习，再于6月启航前往太平洋<ref name="DANFS">{{cite web | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140719043136/http://www.history.navy.mil/danfs/f3/forrestal.htm | url = http://www.history.navy.mil/danfs/f3/forrestal.htm | title = USS Forrestal (CV-59) | publisher = ''Dictionary of American Naval Fighting Ships'' | date = 2007-08-02 | accessdate = 2014-07-19 | archivedate = 2014-07-19}} Regarding use (c), states either Aircraft No. 405 piloted by LCDR Fred D. White or No. 416 piloted by LCDR John McCain was struck by the Zuni. See also {{cite book | last = Stewart | first = Henry P | title = The Impact of the USS Forrestal's 1967 Fire on United States Navy Shipboard Damage Control | publisher = Army Command and General Staff College | location = Fort Leavenworth}}</ref><ref name="freeman" />。麦凯恩的父亲杰克此前已多次升职，于1958年成为[[海军少将|海军少将]]，1963年又当上海军中将<ref name="Alexander-2002" />{{rp|34}}。1967年5月，杰克晋升四星海军上将，成为[[美国海军欧洲舰队|美国海军欧洲舰队]]总司令，驻扎伦敦<ref name="timberg-bio-ch1" />。

=== 投身越战 ===
1967年7月25日，福萊斯特號航空母艦抵达[[北部湾|北部湾]]的[[洋基站|洋基站]]<ref name="DANFS" />，并加入1965至1968年的滚雷行动，针对[[越南民主共和国|北越]]进行[[空中封锁|空中封锁]]和[[战略轰炸|战略轰炸]]<ref name="McCain-Salter-1999" />{{rp|185–186}}。从福莱斯特号发动的[[阿尔法打击_(美国海军)|阿尔法打击]]主要是针对已经选定的特殊目标，如军火库、工厂和桥梁等<ref name="Karaagac">{{cite book | last = Karaagac | first = John | title = John McCain: An Essay in Military and Political History | publisher = Lexington Books | year = 2000 | isbn = 0-7391-0171-4 | pages = 81–82}}</ref>。由于[[越南人民军|北越防空系统]]装备有[[苏联|苏联]]设计和供应的[[地对空导弹|地对空导弹]]、[[防空战|高射炮]]和[[俄罗斯米格航空器集团|米格]]拦截机，这些任务实际上非常危险<ref name="Karaagac" />。麦凯恩参加的前5次空袭北越行动都很顺利<ref name="McCain-Salter-1999" />{{rp|177}}，虽然对一些旁枝末叶的海军法规仍然不放在心上，但他已经成为他人眼中优秀而严谨的飞行员<ref name="freeman" />。麦凯恩和中队的其他飞行员对哥伦比亚特区遥控指挥滚雷行动感到不快<ref name="Karaagac" />，据他之后回忆，出击的具体目标往往限制得太死，以至飞行员不得不反复飞过同一目标实施轰炸，而且大部分飞行员都觉得自己的目标几乎毫无价值。“坦白讲，我们觉得那些平民司令官完全就是白痴，压根儿就不知道要怎么把仗打赢。”<ref name="McCain-Salter-1999" />{{rp|185–186}}

[[File:USS_Forrestal_explosion_29_July_1967.jpg|thumb]]，船员正努力救火。]]

1967年7月29日，福萊斯特號航空母艦的[[舰载机联队|舰载机联队]]正准备发起新一轮攻势，但停在甲板上的一架[[F-4幽灵II战斗机|F-4幽灵II战斗机]]突然意外发射了一枚[[祖尼火箭|祖尼火箭]]<ref name="freeman" />{{rp|102–103}}。火箭击中一架{{lang|en|A}}4天鹰强击机，有可能正是麦凯恩驾驶的那架，也有可能是旁边一架<ref name="DANFS" />。火箭的冲击令天鹰强击机的油箱破裂，油料随即着火，还有两枚炸弹被撞松<ref name="freeman" />{{rp|118}}。麦凯恩之后表示：“我以为我的飞机爆炸了，到处都是火”<ref name="DANFS" />。他爬出驾驶舱，爬向飞机前端的喷口，再从正在加油的探头跳到已经着火的甲板上<ref name="freeman" />{{rp|118}}。麦凯恩的飞行服在他从火焰上滚过时也被点燃，但很快就被他扑灭<ref name="freeman" />{{rp|118}}。正当他前去帮助另一个试图逃生的飞行员时，炸弹爆炸了，麦凯恩被冲击波向后甩出3米远<ref name="nyt073167">{{cite news | archivedate = 2016-01-13 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160113160527/http://query.nytimes.com/gst/abstract.html?res=9B03E2DC1E3AE63ABC4950DFB166838C679EDE | title = Start of Tragedy: Pilot Hears a Blast As He Checks Plane | last = Weinraub | first = Bernard | url = http://query.nytimes.com/gst/abstract.html?res=9B03E2DC1E3AE63ABC4950DFB166838C679EDE | publisher = ''The New York Times'' | date = 1967-07-31}}</ref>，还受了轻伤，腿部和胸口被碎片击中<ref name="lat100608" /><ref name="DANFS" /><ref name="Timberg-1999" />{{rp|72–74}}。接下来，麦凯恩协助舰上其他人员把机库甲板升降机上没有爆炸的炸弹扔进海里，然后同其他飞行员前往航母[[预备室|预备室]]，从[[闭路电视|闭路电视]]查看之后的大火和救火情况<ref name="freeman" />{{rp|170}}。这场火灾夺走134条人命，另有161人受伤，还令至少20架战机被毁，火势直到24小时后才得到控制<ref>{{cite book | last = Stewart | first = Henry P. | title = The Impact of the USS Forrestal's 1967 Fire on United States Navy Shipboard Damage Control | type = Master's Thesis | archivedate = 2014-09-17 | deadurl = no | year = 2004 | publisher = United States Army Command and General Staff College | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140729110143/http://www.dtic.mil/get-tr-doc/pdf?AD=ADA429103 | accessdate = 2016-01-13 | url = http://www.dtic.mil/get-tr-doc/pdf?AD=ADA429103 | location = Fort Leavenworth, KS | format = PDF}}</ref><ref name="DANFS" /><ref name="freeman" />{{rp|228–229}}<ref>包含这场火灾部分镜头的纪录片：{{cite video | url = http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tzgV5QM5fi8 | title = Forrestal | publisher = YouTube | date = 2007-02-24 | accessdate = 2016-01-13 | archive-date = 2020-12-14 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201214033637/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tzgV5QM5fi8 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。火灾次日，麦凯恩在[[胡志明市|西贡]]盛赞那些为挽救甲板上的飞行员而献出生命的战友<ref name="nyt073167" />，他还在接受《[[纽约时报|纽约时报]]》记者[[小雷蒙德·沃尔特·艾伯|小雷蒙德·沃尔特·艾伯]]（{{lang|en|R. W. Apple, Jr.}}）采访时称：“这话很难说出口。但我现在已经见识过这些炸弹和凝固汽油弹会对我们船上的人造成怎样的伤害，所以我也不知道自己还是否愿意继续向北越投弹”<ref name="nyt102867j">{{cite news | title = Adm. McCain's son, Forrestal Survivor, Is Missing in Raid | url = http://query.nytimes.com/gst/abstract.html?res=9D01E2DD173DE63ABC4051DFB667838C679EDE | last = Apple Jr. | first = R. W. | publisher = ''The New York Times'' | date = 1967-10-28 | archivedate = 2015-09-10 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150910140706/http://query.nytimes.com/gst/abstract.html?res=9D01E2DD173DE63ABC4051DFB667838C679EDE}}</ref>。不过他也表示：“我一直想留在海军。我生来就是干这个的，也没有真心考虑过别的职业，只不过对其中的严格管制总不大适应”<ref name="nyt102867j" />。

[[File:Douglas_A-4E_Skyhawk_of_VA-164_in_flight_over_Vietnam_on_21_November_1967_(6430101).jpg|thumb]]，这架强击机隶属[[奥里斯卡尼号航空母舰|奥里斯卡尼号航空母舰]]。]]

随着福莱斯特号开往港口等待修复，麦凯恩自愿加入人手不足的[[奥里斯卡尼号航空母舰|奥里斯卡尼号航空母舰]][[美国海军第163攻击中队|第163“圣徒”攻击中队]]<ref name="Timberg-1999" />{{rp|75}}。这艘航母的甲板之前也发生过火灾<ref name="McCain-Salter-1999" />{{rp|181}}，其攻击中队还是滚雷行动期间损失最惨重的单位之一。“圣徒”以大胆进攻闻名，但也为此付出很大代价<ref name="McCain-Salter-1999" />{{rp|182}}：1967年时，该中队有三分之一的飞行员阵亡或被俘，原有的15架{{lang|en|A}}4强击机均已报销<ref name="McCain-Salter-1999" />{{rp|182}}。麦凯恩在欧洲休养一段时间，还一度返回佛罗里达州[[橙园_(佛罗里达州)|橙园]]的家中静养<ref name="timberg-ns-ch1" />{{rp|99–100}}，再于1967年9月30日到奥里斯卡尼号航母报到<ref name="McCain-Salter-1999" />{{rp|182}}，心中预计次年夏季就可以完成任务回国<ref name="Timberg-1999" />{{rp|76–77}}。他马上就开始主动请缨，要求执行飞行中队接到的最危险任务<ref>{{cite news | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150104114912/http://www.tuscaloosanews.com/article/20080210/NEWS/703947542 | url = http://www.tuscaloosanews.com/article/20080210/NEWS/703947542 | last = DeWitt | first = Robert | title = Support forged in battle | publisher = ''The Tuscaloosa News'' | date = 2008-02-10 | accessdate = 2016-01-14 | archivedate = 2015-01-04}}</ref>。1967年10月，中队飞行员开始以12小时轮班制出击<ref name="McCain-Salter-1999" />{{rp|184}}。10月18日，麦凯恩带领手下分队冒敌军猛烈火力空袭[[海防市|海防市]]的造船厂，之后还因此获颁[[美军荣誉勋章|海军荣誉勋章]]<ref name="milrec-citations">{{cite web | format = PDF | title = John McCain's Navy Records: Citations | archivedate = 2008-11-01 | publisher = United States Navy | accessdate = 2008-05-23 | url = http://www.npc.navy.mil/NR/rdonlyres/330F85C7-5982-4B09-A46A-373964430AFB/0/Document.pdf | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20081101084453/http://www.npc.navy.mil/NR/rdonlyres/330F85C7-5982-4B09-A46A-373964430AFB/0/Document.pdf}}</ref><ref>{{cite news | title = Navy releases McCain's military record | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150801063110/http://www.nbcnews.com/id/24518450/ns/politics-decision_08/t/navy-releases-mccains-military-record/ | last = Kuhnhenn | first = Jim | agency = Associated Press | work = ''NBC News'' | url = http://www.nbcnews.com/id/24518450/ns/politics-decision_08/t/navy-releases-mccains-military-record/ | date = 2008-05-07 | accessdate = 2016-01-14 | archivedate = 2015-08-01}}</ref>。10月25日，麦凯恩出击[[河内市|河内市]]以北有高射炮和地对空导弹火力保护的[[福颜空军基地|福颜空军基地]]取得成功，摧毁地面一架敌机，还打伤另外两架，因此获颁[[铜星勋章|铜星勋章]]<ref name="milrec-citations" />。当时河内周边拥有整个越南战争期间北越最强大的防空火力<ref name="Pribbenow">{{cite journal | first = Merle L. | last = Pribbenow II | date = 2003-01 | title = The -Ology War: Technology and Ideology in the Vietnamese Defense of Hanoi, 1967 | journal = The Journal of Military History | volume = 67 | issue = 1 | pages = 175–200 | format = PDF | doi = 10.1353/jmh.2003.0066 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151111122146/http://muse.jhu.edu/journals/journal_of_military_history/v067/67.1pribbenow.pdf | url = https://muse.jhu.edu/journals/journal_of_military_history/v067/67.1pribbenow.pdf | archivedate = 2015-11-11 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。

=== 战俘 ===

==== 被俘及审讯 ====
[[File:A_4E_barrier_CVA34.jpg|thumb]]上的一架[[A-4天鹰式强击机|A-4天鹰式强击机]]，编号“149959”，6天后，麦凯恩就是同这架强击机一起被敌军击落。]]
1967年10月26日，麦凯恩出发执行第23次空袭任务，同另外19架战机一起突袭河内市中部的[[热力发电厂|热力发电厂]]<ref name="az-pow">{{cite news |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20121205223407/http://www.azcentral.com/news/election/mccain/articles/2007/03/01/20070301mccainbio-chapter3.html |archivedate=2012-12-05 |deadurl=no |first2=Bill |url=http://www.azcentral.com/news/election/mccain/articles/2007/03/01/20070301mccainbio-chapter3.html |title=John McCain Report: Prisoner of War |last1=Nowicki |first1=Dan |last2=Muller |publisher=''The Arizona Republic'' |date=2007-03-01 |accessdate=2016-01-14 }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=In pictures, Vietnam visit, McCain memorial |publisher=BBC News |accessdate=2016-01-14 |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20120711022319/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/shared/spl/hi/pop_ups/06/asia_pac_vietnam_visit/html/4.stm |archivedate=2012-07-11 |deadurl=no |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/shared/spl/hi/pop_ups/06/asia_pac_vietnam_visit/html/4.stm }}</ref>，由于担心造成[[附带损害|附带损害]]，美国此前几乎没有把这里作为袭击目标<ref name="Pribbenow" />。麦凯恩在正午前夕抵达目标附近，然后从约2700米高空下降至约1200米逼近目标<ref name="wapo100508">{{cite news |accessdate=2016-01-14 |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20130205222626/http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2008/10/04/AR2008100402351_pf.html |url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2008/10/04/AR2008100402351_pf.html |title=In Ordeal as Captive, Character Was Shaped |last=Dobbs |first=Michael |publisher=''The Washington Post'' |date=2008-10-05 |archivedate=2013-02-05 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>，这时，{{lang|en|A4}}强击机的警报系统报告他已被敌军[[火控雷达|火控雷达]]追踪<ref name="Timberg-1999" />{{rp|78}}。但是，麦凯恩和其他遇到类似情况的美军飞行员一样继续执行轰炸任务<ref name="lat100608" />，他驾驶飞机继续下降，在距地面约1000米的空中发射炸弹<ref name="McCain-Salter-1999" />{{rp|188}}<ref>{{cite news | url = http://www.tuscaloosanews.com/article/20080210/NEWS/703947542 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150104114912/http://www.tuscaloosanews.com/article/20080210/NEWS/703947542 | deadurl = no | title = Support forged in battle | publisher = ''The Tuscaloosa News'' | date = 2008-02-10 | accessdate = 2016-01-14 | archivedate = 2015-01-04}}</ref>。但就在他开始爬升时，战机的机翼被北越防空司令部第61营发射的苏制[[S-75导弹|SA-2]]防空导弹炸毁<ref name="Pribbenow" /><ref name="wapo100508" />。当时指挥第61营击落麦凯恩战机的是营长阮兰<ref name="wapo100508" />和火力控制指挥阮禤代中尉<ref name="Pribbenow" /><ref name="wapo100508" />。麦凯恩之后因被击落而获得[[飞行优异十字勋章|飞行优异十字勋章]]<ref name="milrec-citations" />，阮禤代则被授予越南人民军英雄称号<ref name="Pribbenow" />。数十年后，前[[苏联红军|苏联红军]]中尉尤里·特鲁塞克钦（{{lang|en|Yuri Trushechkin}}）声称他正是当年击落麦凯恩的导弹制导军官<ref>{{cite news | url = https://www.rt.com/news/i-shot-down-mccain-soviet-soldier/ | title = I shot down McCain - Soviet soldier | publisher = Russia Today | date = 2008-12-11 | accessdate = 2016-01-14 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130218092951/http://rt.com/news/i-shot-down-mccain-soviet-soldier/ | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2013-02-18}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Soviet Officer Who Shot Down John McCain in Vietnam Dies |url=http://politicom.moldova.org/news/soviet-officer-who-shot-down-john-mccain-in-vietnam-dies-177670-eng.html |first=Paul |publisher=Window on Eurasia for Moldova.org |date=2009-01-19 |accessdate=2012-02-16 |last=Goble |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120216060051/http://politicom.moldova.org/news/soviet-officer-who-shot-down-john-mccain-in-vietnam-dies-177670-eng.html |archivedate=2012-02-16 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。无论从任何角度来说，这次空袭行动都是失败的，有3架美国海军战机被击落，但目标发电厂完好无损<ref name="wapo100508" />。

[[File:Vietcapturejm01.jpg|thumb]]的麦凯恩被北越平民拖出，之后不久就沦为北越[[战俘|战俘]]<ref>{{cite web | title = John McCain (center) being captured by Vietnamese civilians in Truc Bach Lake near Hanoi Vietnam. | url= http://memory.loc.gov/diglib/vhp/story/loc.natlib.afc2001001.07736/enlarge?ID=ph0003001&page=1 | publisher = Library of Congress | date = 2004-05-26 | accessdate = 2016-01-14 | archivedate = 2015-11-06 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151106220548/http://memory.loc.gov/diglib/vhp/story/loc.natlib.afc2001001.07736/enlarge?ID=ph0003001&page=1 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。]]

麦凯恩的战机以近乎垂直的角度[[尾旋|高速旋转下坠]]<ref name="usnwr73">{{cite news | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151229144627/http://www.usnews.com/news/articles/2008/01/28/john-mccain-prisoner-of-war-a-first-person-account | title = How the POW's Fought Back | author = Lieut. Commander John S. McCain III, United States Navy | url= http://www.usnews.com/news/articles/2008/01/28/john-mccain-prisoner-of-war-a-first-person-account | publisher = ''U.S. News & World Report'' | date = 1973-05-14 | archivedate = 2015-12-29}} (reposted under title "John McCain, Prisoner of War: A First-Person Account", 2008-01-28). Reprinted in {{cite book | last = Library of America staff | title = Reporting Vietnam, Part Two: American Journalism 1969–1975 | publisher = The Library of America | year=1998 | isbn=1-883011-59-0 | pages = 434–463}} Used to support direct quotes from McCain, or to fill in details not given by other sources.</ref><ref name="Rochester-Kiley-1999">{{cite book | last1 = Rochester | first1 = Stuart I. | last2 = Kiley | first2 = Frederick | title = Honor Bound: American Prisoners of War in Southeast Asia, 1961–1973 | url = https://archive.org/details/honorboundameric0000roch | publisher = Naval Institute Press | year = 1999 | location = Annapolis, Maryland | isbn = 1-55750-694-9}}</ref>{{rp|360}}，[[弹射椅|弹射椅]]的力道将麦凯恩撞晕过去，他的右臂有三处骨折，左臂和右腿膝盖也因此骨折<ref name="Rochester-Kiley-1999" />{{rp|360}}<ref name="time051408">{{cite news|url=http://content.time.com/time/magazine/article/0,9171,1806794,00.html |title=How Healthy Is John McCain? |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150418055740/http://content.time.com/time/magazine/article/0%2C9171%2C1806794%2C00.html |last1=Scherer |first1=Michael |last2=Park |first2=Alice |publisher=''[[时代_(杂志)|Time]]'' |date=2008-05-14 |accessdate=2016-01-15 |archivedate=2015-04-18 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。麦凯恩和降落伞一起掉入河内市的[[竹帛湖|竹帛湖]]，这时他虽然恢复知觉，但手臂却不听使唤，无法自救，身上的装备也令他逐渐下沉<ref name="Timberg-1999" />{{rp|78}}，最后用牙齿才成功打开[[救生衣|救生衣]]<ref name="Timberg-1999" />{{rp|78}}。多名北越人下水将他拖上岸，这些人的身份尚无定论<ref>See also the 2008-10-05 Dobbs ''Washington Post'' story, which credits paper factory worker Tran Lua.</ref><ref>{{cite news | date = 2000-02-24 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090703215646/http://quest.cjonline.com/stories/022400/gen_rescuer.shtml | deadurl = yes | url = http://quest.cjonline.com/stories/022400/gen_rescuer.shtml | title = McCain's Vietnam rescuer talks | publisher = Associated Press | archivedate = 2009-07-03 | accessdate = 2009-07-03}}</ref><ref name="Alexander-2002" />{{rp|47–49}}<ref>{{cite news | title = Wartime rescuer of John McCain dies a forgotten hero | last = Parry | first = Simon | agency = Deutsche Presse-Agentur | publisher = ''Thaindian News'' | date = 2008-06-27 | accessdate = 2016-01-15 | url = http://www.thaindian.com/newsportal/world-news/wartime-rescuer-of-john-mccain-dies-a-forgotten-hero_10064998.html | archive-date = 2018-08-26 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180826113332/http://www.thaindian.com/newsportal/world-news/wartime-rescuer-of-john-mccain-dies-a-forgotten-hero_10064998.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>。许多人围上前来，朝麦凯恩吐唾沫、用脚踢他，还剥掉他的衣服，他的左肩也被枪托打成[[粉碎性骨折|粉碎性骨折]]，左脚和腹部还被刺伤<ref name="Timberg-1999" />{{rp|78}}<ref name="Rochester-Kiley-1999" />{{rp|360}}<ref name="time051408" />。接下来麦凯恩被送到河内的[[火炉监狱|火炉监狱]]，美国战俘戏称这所监狱是“河内希尔顿酒店”<ref name="Hubbell-1976" />{{rp|363}}。

同其他战俘一样，麦凯恩的身体状况在抵达火炉监狱时也很差<ref name="Hubbell-1976">{{cite book | last = Hubbell | first = John G. | title = P.O.W.: A Definitive History of the American Prisoner-Of-War Experience in Vietnam, 1964–1973 | url = https://archive.org/details/powdefinitivehis00hubb | publisher = Reader's Digest Press | year = 1976 | location = New York | isbn = 0-88349-091-9}}</ref>{{rp|363}}。北越方面要求他泄露军事情报，否则不会提供医疗救助，面对殴打和审讯，麦凯恩说出的只有自己的姓名、军衔、生日和编号<ref name="Hubbell-1976" />{{rp|364}}<ref name="Timberg-1999" />{{rp|79}}，根据[[日内瓦公约|日内瓦公约]]，战俘应当告知这些信息，而美军行为准则中也只允许军人被俘后向敌国透露这些内容<ref name="wapo100508" />。不久后，麦凯恩觉得自己已濒临死亡，他要求越方送他到医院救治，表示愿提供更多情报<ref name="Hubbell-1976" />{{rp|364}}，打算在得到治疗后要求推迟审问<ref name="Timberg-1999" />{{rp|80}}。监狱医生前来查看，但觉得麦凯恩的伤势太重，他已无力回天<ref name="Hubbell-1976" />{{rp|364}}。但是，北越当局发现麦凯恩的父亲原来是美国的海军上将，于是将他送医<ref name="Hubbell-1976" />{{rp|364}}，还称他是“皇太子”<ref name="Hubbell-1976" />{{rp|363}}。麦凯恩的战机被击落仅两天后，他沦为战俘的消息就成为《[[纽约时报|纽约时报]]》<ref name="nyt102867j" />和《[[华盛顿邮报|华盛顿邮报]]》的头条新闻<ref>{{cite news | title = Admiral's Son Captured in Hanoi Raid | agency = Associated Press | publisher = ''The Washington Post'' | date = 1967-10-28}}</ref>。麦凯恩还在医院时，严刑逼供再度降临，他告诉敌方自己所在中队及航母的名称，还有之前空袭的预定目标<ref name="McCain-Salter-1999" />{{rp|193–194}}。之后的两个多星期里，北越官媒《[[人民报_(越南)|人民报]]》发表多篇文章，其中除上述信息外，还包括麦凯恩的一些私人信息，另有部分据称是麦凯恩对战争进程看法的内容<ref name="wapo100508" />。这些内容还出现在古巴[[拉美通讯社|拉美通讯社]]的多封稿件中<ref>{{cite web | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120213223111/http://www.foia.cia.gov/search.asp?pageNumber=1&txtSearch=mccain&sortOrder=ASC | url = http://www.foia.cia.gov/search.asp?pageNumber=1&txtSearch=mccain&sortOrder=ASC | title = Freedom of Information Act: Search Results (McCain) | publisher = Central Intelligence Agency | accessdate = 2012-02-13 | format = barely readable scans | archivedate = 2012-02-13}}[[中央情报局外国广播信息处|中央情报局外国广播信息处]]截获多种文件，涉及范围包括麦凯恩被俘相关的盟军部署或北越方面部署。[[中央情报局|中央情报局]]之后根据《[[信息自由法_(美国)|信息自由法]]》规定公布这些文件。</ref>。虽然麦凯恩当时觉得这些“情报”对北越没有任何实际价值，但向敌军透露这些信息仍然有违军队的行为准则，之后他也对此表示悔不当初<ref name="McCain-Salter-1999" />{{rp|198}}。北越逼迫他披露之后美军的轰炸目标，麦凯恩于是“交待”了多个已被炸过的城市，敌方还要求他透露所在中队其他飞行员的姓名，但麦凯恩所说的实际上都是[[绿湾包装工|绿湾包装工]]美式足球队的进攻球员<ref name="McCain-Salter-1999" />{{rp|193–194}}<ref name="nyt121505">{{cite news | url = http://www.nytimes.com/2005/12/15/politics/mccain-pays-a-tribute-at-funeral-of-expow.html | title = McCain Pays a Tribute at Funeral of Ex-P.O.W. | last = Shane | first = Scott | publisher = ''The New York Times'' | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150529183109/http://www.nytimes.com/2005/12/15/politics/mccain-pays-a-tribute-at-funeral-of-expow.html | date = 2005-12-15 | accessdate = 2016-01-14 | archivedate = 2015-05-29}}</ref>。

